Ranger Help for: gaia's eyes
=============================

SYNTAX:      reyes
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   10
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  religious

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to use Gaia's sight to view distant rooms
without physically traveling to them. The Ranger enters a trance-like
state and sees through the eyes of nature itself. The range of the
remote viewing scales with the Ranger's guild level and wisdom. This
is useful for scouting ahead or locating specific areas without
putting the Ranger in danger.
